Package org.logevents.util

Class JsonUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.util.JsonUtil
  • public class JsonUtil
extends Object
    A utility class for minimal JSON functionality. Prints a Map<String, Object> as JSON, supporting Map, Iterable, String, Number and Boolean. This class is stand alone and only depends on Java. It can be copied-and- pasted into existing project. This class is independently shared under the BSD license 2.0.
    Author:
    johannes@brodwall.com (Johannes Brodwall)
